                    <li>Horsepower =3D (300 =C3=97 4,500) =C3=B7 5,252</li>
                    <li>Horsepower =3D 1,350,000 =C3=B7 5,252</li>
                    <li><strong>Result =3D 257.1 HP</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

